To get creator points in geometry dash, you need to create and publish levels that other players enjoy. The more levels you create and the more players that play them, the more creator points you will earn. You can also earn creator points by being featured on the Featured Levels list.

Here are some tips for getting creator points in geometry dash:

Create levels that are challenging but fair. Players will be more likely to play your levels if they are fun and rewarding.
Make sure your levels are well-designed and visually appealing. Players will be more likely to play your levels if they look good.
Promote your levels on social media and forums. The more people that know about your levels, the more likely they are to play them.

If you follow these tips, you will be well on your way to earning creator points in geometry dash!
